{"tid":307364,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想買部即影即有","createTime":"2017-07-03T10:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T11:15:57.000Z","uid":58093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8afa6b072b30d7a29b07b40d7c0d38560d627f4e","tid":307364,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"想買部好似下面圖呢款既即影即有,平時帶出街有野想影可以影下<br />\n巴絲有冇好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/180533_28a43d196cb492627376163e933e138a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F180533_28a43d196cb492627376163e933e138a.jpg&h=1c7bb6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/180646_65bc4dfd5be1d4e2923b665d13ea39e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F180646_65bc4dfd5be1d4e2923b665d13ea39e1.jpg&h=e0637c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申 新手想得閒影下難忘畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4c1412d4742994354d03e849ad490b36627a6e","tid":307364,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"寶麗萊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有買過一部 但覺得好難影(不過對上一次用已經有一段日子 可能依架啲相紙有出改良版 好用咗<br />\n而且有可能係因為我技術差<br />\n我記得旺角有專賣呢啲即影即有嘅舖頭 但價錢貴過出面<br />\n不過叫係方便新手(我覺得"},{"pid":"6c6b2e261bea75616d01f8ffe6f178c59606be66","tid":307364,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"頭先search咗 原來叫 SHOWA 昭和相機店<br />\n不過我覺得佢啲嘢價錢唔平 可以去睇下啲款 買就建議諗下先<br />\n大概1-2兩年前 我喺佢到買咗呢部<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/184516_ba5660ddbab55de6742edf85e8ecfff4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F184516_ba5660ddbab55de6742edf85e8ecfff4.jpg&h=a2354d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過相紙太貴 我有點窮 後尾就冇乜點用<br />\n見到呢個post又想拎返出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我啲技術會進步下"},{"pid":"2e1bcf15d5925ef527cdd2a8dc02f818372f83ad","tid":307364,"uid":45538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"如果係寶麗萊既話image playground應該會平啲<br />\n中環同旺角都有鋪頭<br />\n不過如果巴打唔急既話可以等大學mega sell有時會請佢擺檔 平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 有部600<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d72b23d774f761d34b2fb5951aafe3891ad722","tid":307364,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"用呢d影相有冇咩心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a79cf422783b5b230d70a2689eb4f593410c7c","tid":307364,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先search咗 原來叫 SHOWA 昭和相機店<br />\n不過我覺得佢啲嘢價錢唔平 可以去睇下啲款 買就建議諗下先<br />\n大概1-2兩年前 我喺佢到買咗呢部<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/184516_ba5660ddbab55de6742edf85e8ecfff4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F184516_ba5660ddbab55de6742edf85e8ecfff4.jpg&h=a2354d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過相紙太貴 我有點窮 後尾就冇乜點用<br />\n見到呢個post又想拎返出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我啲技術會進步下</blockquote><br />\n好想買一部，出街見到野想影可以影下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844fc3c52cfe506457ae930e006e4301372349e5","tid":307364,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:15:57.000Z","msg":"如果出街影建議你俾多少少錢買部有得關自動閃光燈嘅<br />\n唔係下下影相都勁閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔方便<br />\n至於技巧 我冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但熟能生巧<br />\n不過百幾蚊一盒相紙 仲要得八張 都貴架"}]}